        {
            "title": "美股日誌｜ 動盪一周終結　油價全星期狂升35%",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"美股日誌｜ 動盪一周終結 油價全星期狂升35%\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"659\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/V80IwHgCOc2XuFxBxcc4tQ--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTY1OQ--/https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2026-03/b773aef0-19ab-11f1-b3b3-efcef343179f\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\">美股日誌｜ 動盪一周終結 油價全星期狂升35%</figcaption></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">3月6日，星期五。關鍵的每月就業報告意外轉弱，市場對通脹的憂慮升溫，三大指數皆下跌。美股經歷動盪一周後，好消息是美股明天喘定。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">道指下跌0.9%，即逾450點，是跌幅最少的指數；以科技股為主的納指數下跌約1.6%；標普500指數下跌1.3%。三大指數全周均錄得跌幅，標普500指數累跌2%，道指更挫3%，納指則跌約1%。而由年初至今亦已轉為下跌。</p><blockquote class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull\" style=\"padding-bottom:min(300px, undefined%)\"></div></blockquote><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">因霍爾木茲海峽油輪運輸幾乎陷入停滯，市場擔心波斯灣出口國在儲存空間耗盡後可能被迫減產。同時，美國與以色列對伊朗的戰事仍未見緩和跡象，特朗普今天表示，解決衝突的唯一途徑是「無條件投降」。油價升至逾90元，全星期累計升幅高達35%。</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-f4baba21-8022-4470-a2fa-a4e0070d16ce-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"cpos:1;pos:1\" data-ylk=\"slk:下載Yahoo財經APP;cpos:1;pos:1;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://mobile.yahoo.com/finance?pid=editorial&amp;c=HK_Acquisition_YMktg_Evergreen_article_&amp;af_sub1=Acquisition&amp;af_sub2=HK_YMktg&amp;af_sub4=1058&amp;af_sub5=article__Banner_&amp;uuid=eDFkEhESdIhPGYRE2850\">下載Yahoo財經APP</a></p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">美股外幣即時報價 多國新聞任睇</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">3月6日（星期五）市况</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">l<a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"cpos:2;pos:1\" data-ylk=\"slk:道瓊斯指數;cpos:2;pos:1;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/quote/%5EDJI\"> 道瓊斯指數</a> 跌453.19點或0.95%，報47,501.55點。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">l<a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"cpos:3;pos:1\" data-ylk=\"slk:標普500指數;cpos:3;pos:1;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/quote/%5EGSPC\"> 標普500指數</a> 跌90.69點或1.33%，報6,740.02點。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">l<a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"cpos:4;pos:1\" data-ylk=\"slk:納斯達克指數;cpos:4;pos:1;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/quote/%5EIXIC\"> 納斯達克指數</a> 跌361.31點或1.59%，報22,387.68點。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">l<a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"cpos:5;pos:1\" data-ylk=\"slk:紐約4月期油;cpos:5;pos:1;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/quote/CL=F\"> 紐約4月期油</a> 收報91.27美元一桶，升10.26美元或12.67%。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">l<a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"cpos:6;pos:1\" data-ylk=\"slk:紐約4月期金;cpos:6;pos:1;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/quote/GC=F\"> 紐約4月期金</a> 收報5,181.3美元一盎司，升102.6美元或2.02%。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">l<a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"cpos:7;pos:1\" data-ylk=\"slk:比特幣;cpos:7;pos:1;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/quote/BTC-USD/\"> 比特幣</a> 截至美東時間下午4時報68,119.67美元，跌3,128.45美元或4.39%</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">l<a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"cpos:8;pos:1\" data-ylk=\"slk:美國10年期國債息率;cpos:8;pos:1;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/quote/%5ETNX\"> 美國10年期國債息率</a> 收報4.133厘。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">2月就業報告顯示，非農就業職位意外減少92,000個，遠遜於市場預期的新增55,000個；失業率亦上升至4.4%。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">勞動市場轉弱，加上中東衝突推高油價，令市場憂慮出現滯脹，亦即經濟增長疲弱與通脹上升同時出現。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">油價狂升，航空股最為受壓，<a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"cpos:9;pos:1\" data-ylk=\"slk:美國航空;cpos:9;pos:1;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/quote/AAL/\">美國航空</a>(AAL.US)挫5.2%，美聯航(UAL.US)、<a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"cpos:10;pos:1\" data-ylk=\"slk:達美航空;cpos:10;pos:1;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/quote/DAL/\">達美航空</a>(DAL.US)均跌逾3%。<a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"cpos:11;pos:1\" data-ylk=\"slk:Caterpillar;cpos:11;pos:1;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/quote/CAT/\">Caterpillar</a>(CAT.US)跌3.6%。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">大型科技股走弱，<a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"cpos:12;pos:1\" data-ylk=\"slk:英偉達;cpos:12;pos:1;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/quote/NVDA/\">英偉達</a>(NVDA.US)挫3%，<a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"cpos:13;pos:1\" data-ylk=\"slk:Meta;cpos:13;pos:1;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/quote/META/\">Meta</a>(META.US)、<a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"cpos:14;pos:1\" data-ylk=\"slk:亞馬遜;cpos:14;pos:1;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/quote/AMZN/\">亞馬遜</a>(AMZN.US)、特斯拉(TSLA.US)均跌逾2%，<a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"cpos:15;pos:1\" data-ylk=\"slk:蘋果;cpos:15;pos:1;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/quote/AAPL/\">蘋果</a>(AAPL.US)、Alphabet(GOOG.US)跌約1%。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">美國總統特普在周五呼籲伊朗「無條件投降」，亦會晤多家美國主要國防承包商高層，包括<a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"cpos:16;pos:1\" data-ylk=\"slk:Lockheed Martin;cpos:16;pos:1;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/quote/LMT/\">Lockheed Martin</a>(LMT.US)、<a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"cpos:17;pos:1\" data-ylk=\"slk:波音;cpos:17;pos:1;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/quote/BA/\">波音</a>(BA.US)、<a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"cpos:18;pos:1\" data-ylk=\"slk:RTX;cpos:18;pos:1;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/quote/RTX/\">RTX</a>(RTX.US)及<a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"cpos:19;pos:1\" data-ylk=\"slk:Northrop Grumman;cpos:19;pos:1;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/quote/NOC/\">Northrop Grumman</a>(NOC.US)等軍工商。相關軍工股普遍升約2%。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">外界憂慮隨著對伊朗戰事持續接近一周且未見結束跡象，美軍武器庫存正逐步消耗，白宮則淡化武器庫存下降的憂慮，強調美軍軍火庫存充足。</p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E7%BE%8E%E8%82%A1%E6%97%A5%E8%AA%8C%EF%BD%9C-%E5%8B%95%E7%9B%AA%E4%B8%80%E5%91%A8%E7%B5%82%E7%B5%90-%E6%B2%B9%E5%83%B9%E5%85%A8%E6%98%9F%E6%9C%9F%E7%8B%82%E5%8D%8735-223632886.html",
            "pub_date": "2026-03-07 10:18:40",
            "source": "yahoo_finance_asia",
            "kind": 1,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "人行：無意藉滙率貶值取貿易優勢  今年促經濟穩增長 靈活運用降準減息",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"548\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/0ONprM50CIJFuA1hywihMg--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTU0OA--/https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2026-03/9db132c0-19ca-11f1-951d-55f54c545e7e\" width=\"960\"/></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">《政府工作報告》明確今年繼續實施適度寬鬆的貨幣政策，人行行長潘功勝周五（6日）表示，人行今年把促進經濟穩定增長、物價合理回升作為貨幣政策重要考量，靈活高效運用降準減息等多種貨幣政策工具。當局擬綜合運用短中長期政策工具，保持市場流動性充裕，並根據經濟金融形勢變化和宏觀經濟運行情況，引導和調控利率水平，促進社會融資成本低位運行。針對近期人民幣升值，潘功勝強調，中國無意通過滙率貶值獲取貿易競爭優勢。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><strong>潘功勝：保持市場流動性充裕</strong></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">十四屆全國人大四次會議經濟主題記者會周五舉行，國家發展改革委、財政部、商務部、人民銀行、中國證監會官員均有出席並回答提問。潘功勝在會上稱，人行將發揮增量政策和存量政策、貨幣政策與財政政策的集成、協同效應，為「十五五」良好開局營造良好的貨幣金融環境。數量型貨幣政策上，除了存款準備金外，工具箱還包括逆回購、中期借貸便利（MLF）、買賣國債等公開市場操作工具，人行會綜合運用這些工具，保持市場流動性充裕，使社會融資規模、貨幣供應量增長匹配經濟增長、價格總水平的預期目標。</p><div class=\"bg-toast-background -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0 lg:mx-auto lg:w-[300px] lg:pb-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-e593d817-6eef-33bb-9b25-60f43a6e562e-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">利率方面，潘功勝說，將強化利率政策執行和監督，對於一些不合理、容易削減貨幣政策傳導的市場行為加強規範，並要求銀行向企業明確展示貸款年化綜合融資成本，規範融資中間費用。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">參考今年1月，內地社會融資規模按年增長8.2%，廣義貨幣（M2）按年增長9%，當月新發放企業貸款和個人住房貸款加權平均利率分別約3.2%、3.1%，處於歷史低位水平。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">會上，潘功勝亦談及滙率問題，今年以來人民幣對美元升值，他認為與內地經濟持續向好、美滙指數走弱、企業季節性結滙等有關，目前人民幣對美元雙邊滙率水平處於近年中值區間。「中國沒有必要，也無意通過滙率貶值獲取貿易競爭優勢。人民銀行的立場始終是清晰的，堅持市場在滙率形成之中的決定性作用，保持滙率彈性，加強預期引導，保持人民幣滙率在合理均衡水平上的基本穩定。」</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">針對「十五五」中長期貨幣政策體系構建，潘功勝表明，當前貨幣政策採用數量型和價格型調控並行方式，未來將逐步淡化數量型中介目標，把金融總量更多作為觀測性、參考性、預期性指標，為更好發揮利率調控的作用創造條件。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><strong>2500億超長期特別國債 撐舊換新</strong></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">另一方面，擴內需是內地今年重點任務。商務部部長王文濤稱，政府今年安排超長期特別國債2500億元人民幣支持消費品以舊換新，商務部擬進一步優化實施機制，重點支持綠色智能商品和線下實體零售，「為新產業、新賽道換出市場空間、增添活力。」</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">去年中國貿易順差創下新高，接近1.2萬億美元，《政府工作報告》提到的「積極擴大進口，推動貿易平衡發展」也引起外界關注。王文濤認為，「出口和進口就像一輛車的兩個輪子，這兩個輪子愈平衡，這輛車就開得愈平穩、走得愈遠。」他續說，中國是全球第二大進口市場，中等收入群體規模不斷壯大，因此市場潛力還很大，而且屬主動開放的市場。中國將發揮超大規模市場優勢，擴大農產品、優質消費品、先進技術設備和關鍵零部件等進口。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">至於吸引外資，王文濤說，現時不少外資企業把中國市場看作「健身房」和「試驗場」，「很多外資企業到中國來，就像健身房一樣強身健體，與國內企業公平競爭」，中國擁有超大規模市場與豐富場景，成為外資企業各種創新研發的試驗場、應用場。</p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E4%BA%BA%E8%A1%8C-%E7%84%A1%E6%84%8F%E8%97%89%E6%BB%99%E7%8E%87%E8%B2%B6%E5%80%BC%E5%8F%96%E8%B2%BF%E6%98%93%E5%84%AA%E5%8B%A2-%E4%BB%8A%E5%B9%B4%E4%BF%83%E7%B6%93%E6%BF%9F%E7%A9%A9%E5%A2%9E%E9%95%B7-%E9%9D%88%E6%B4%BB%E9%81%8B%E7%94%A8%E9%99%8D%E6%BA%96%E6%B8%9B%E6%81%AF-184000447.html",
